               <msContents>
                  <summary/>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i0">
                     <locus from="1r" to="14r">1r-14r</locus>
                     <textLang xml:lang="ar">Arabic</textLang>
                     <title ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT0049IHA#s10IHA">قران, Third ǧuz’ (3/30)</title>
                     <incipit xml:lang="ar">
                        <locus target="#1r">-1r</locus>تِلْكَ الرُّسُلُ فَضَّلْنَا بَعْضَهُمْ عَلَي بَعْضٍ مِنْهُمْ مَّن كَلَّمَ اللهُ</incipit>
                     <explicit xml:lang="ar">
                        <locus target="#14r">-14r</locus>وَّلَوْ اَفْتَدَيْ بِهِ أُوْلَيِكَ لَهُمْ عَذَابٌ أَلِيْمٌ وَّمَا لَهُمْ مِّنْ نَّاصِريْنَ </explicit>
                     <note>2:253-3:91. No verse markers on folios 1v-2r. On the rest of the folios red triple dots as verse markers. Large script (takbīr, 6r). Some extensions of words and letters into the margin. Words left incomplete at the end of a line, sometimes without diacritics or vocalization, and completed or written in full on the following line. Sign or acronyms used to fill out the line and meet the margin. Deletions, sometimes followed by the correct version. Corrections in the margins. Catchwords from another hand. Repairs (3r, 13v).</note>
                     <note/>
                  </msItem>
               </msContents>
